{"parse":{"title":"Zul'Gurub","pageid":305952,"wikitext":{"*":"{{Stub/Location}}\n{{infobox instance\n|name=Zul'Gurub\n|aka=ZG\n|ss=Zul'Gurub.png\n|caption=loading screen\n|loc=Northeastern [[Northern Stranglethorn]]\n|race={{Race|Troll}}<br /> {{Race|Blood elf}}\n|boss={{mob|Jin'do the Godbreaker|boss=}}\n|type=Dungeon\n|level=85\n|minlevel=85\n|minilvl=346\n|players=5\n|bosses={{Zul'Gurub}}\n}}\n:''For the outdoor subzone and history of the zone of the same name, see [[Zul'Gurub (lore)]]. For the old raid instance, see [[Zul'Gurub (raid)]].''\nThe [[troll]] city of '''Zul'Gurub''' re-opened in [[Patch 4.1]] as 5-man, level 85, [[heroic mode]] [[instance]].\n\n== Bosses ==\n:''Full boss strategies do not belong in this section or its subsections. Only key abilities or adds should be listed.''\n=== {{mob|boss=|High Priest Venoxis}} ===\n=== {{mob|boss=|Bloodlord Mandokir}} ===\n;Sub-boss\n* {{mob|boss=|Ohgan}}, Mandokir's raptor\n\n=== The [[Cache of Madness]] ===\n* {{mob|boss=|Hazza'rah}} (summoned)\n* {{mob|boss=|Renataki}} (summoned)\n* {{mob|boss=|Wushoolay}} (summoned)\n* {{mob|boss=|Gri'lek}} (summoned)\n\n=== {{mob|boss=|High Priestess Kilnara}} ===\n=== {{mob|boss=|Zanzil (boss)||Zanzil}} ===\n=== {{mob|boss=|Jin'do the Godbreaker}} ===\n\n== Gallery ==\n<gallery>\nFile:WorldMap-ZulGurub1.jpg|Phase 1\nFile:WorldMap-ZulGurub2.jpg|Phase 2\nZul\u00b4Gurub Portal.jpg|Open door to enter instance\n</gallery>\n\n== Quests ==\n*{{questlong|Neutral|1<small>Daily Dungeon</small>|Zul'Aman Voodoo}}\n*{{questlong|Neutral|1<small>Daily Dungeon</small>|Zul'Gurub Voodoo}}\n*{{questlong|Alliance|85|A Shiny Reward (Alliance)|A Shiny Reward}}\n*{{questlong|Horde|85|A Shiny Reward (Horde)|A Shiny Reward}}\n*{{questlong|Neutral|85|An Old Friend}}\n*{{questlong|Neutral|85D|Break Their Spirits}}\n*{{questlong|Neutral|85D|Secondary Targets}}\n*{{questlong|Neutral|85D|The Beasts Within}}\n*{{questlong|Alliance|85H|Booty Bay's Interests (Alliance)|Booty Bay's Interests}}\n*{{questlong|Horde|85H|Booty Bay's Interests (Horde)|Booty Bay's Interests}}\n*{{questlong|Neutral|85H|Break the Godbreaker}}\n\n== Videos ==\n[[File:Cataclysm - Patch 4.1 Rise of the Zandalari|thumb|left|300 px]]\n[[File:How to find the entrance to Zul 'gurub - World of Warcraft|thumb|right|300 px]]\n[[File:How to Solo Zul'Aman & Zul'Gurub HC MoP|thumb|left|300 px]]\n[[File:LoD's Zul'Gurub Guide|thumb|right|300 px]]\n{{Clr}}\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Patch 4.1]]\n* [[Zul'Aman]]\n\n== External links ==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-zone|1977}}\n;Subzone\n{{elinks-zone|19}}\n;Info\n{{elink|type=wowinsider|link=http://wow.joystiq.com/2011/08/22/does-the-rise-of-the-zandalari-dungeon-tier-serve-a-purpose/|desc=Does the Rise of the Zandalari dungeon tier serve a purpose?|bydate=by {{wowinsider|Matthew Rossi}} Aug 22nd 2011 at 1:00PM}}\n;Guides\n{{elink|icon=icyveinscom|site=Icy Veins|link=http://www.icy-veins.com/zul-gurub-heroic-dungeon|desc=Zul'Gurub Guide (Cataclysm, patch 4.1)}}\n{{elink|icon=wowheadnews|site=Wowhead News|link=http://www.wowheadnews.com/blog=187922/in-depth-boss-strategies-for-zulaman-and-zulgurub|desc=In-depth Boss Strategies for Zul'Aman and Zul'Gurub|bydate=by [http://www.wowheadnews.com/blog&user=Ashelia Ashelia] 4/27/2011 9:18 AM}}\n{{elink|type=wowinsider|link=http://wow.joystiq.com/2011/04/26/patch-4-1-guide-to-the-new-zulgurub/|desc=Patch 4.1: Guide to the new Zul'Gurub|bydate=by [http://wow.joystiq.com/bloggers/allison-robert/ Allison Robert] Apr 26th 2011 at 2:00PM }}\n;Old forum discussion\n{{elink|type=bnetwowus|site=Official General Discussion forum (US)|link=http://us.battle.net/wow/en/forum/topic/2140270264#6|desc=Stop complaining about ZA and ZG|bydate=#6 [[Zarhym]] 3/1/11 9:34 PM}}\n{{elink|type=bnetwowus|site=Official Public Test Realm forum (EU)|link=http: